									<h1>FAQs</h1>
                                     <p style="text-align:justify;">
                                    <b>1. What's pricing in Shahapur area and pricing of The White Villas and how are THE WHITE VILLAS different ?</b><br><br />

                                    In Shahapur , the flats start from 2800 per sq ft to 3500 per sq ft. These are generally regular flats and small sized apartments with no amenities. <br>
                                    And villa cost varies according to design, quality & finish, depending on location & quality / amenities provided. This is the only designer project in that 167km stretch. This is limited edition Mediterranean styled 43 designer villas in a fully developed 2 acre gated community designed by Ms. Sussanne Khan as a first phase.<br>
                                    The No. of Villas are restricted to only 43 in these 2 acres , for imparting luxury comfort to the prospective buyers. <br />
                                    Having the trademark and design of the internationally acclaimed Ms. Susanne Khan, is one of the most highlighting points of the project. <br />
                                    It's the only designer villa project on the 167 km stretch from Mumbai to Nashik which has a clear height of 11 feet on the ground floor and a maximum clear height of 18 feet and minimum 11 feet height at the lowest level on the first floor , with two bedrooms on the first floor. Both have open to sky terraces giving extended feel of the bedrooms. <br>
                                    The ground floor has a large and spacious living room , one guest bedroom which extends into rear open area ,giving a feel of the open area within the bedroom and a kitchen with separate service area . All the Three side open space can be accessed from the living room, the bedroom and the Kitchen. Which is again a very unique feature to be enjoyed with- the villa. <br>
                                    All rooms have big size French Windows with 8 feet height .  The villa has an independent compound wall with one covered car park in the front  entrance of the villa. <br />
                                    The 3BHK villa comes with a ownership of a 1200  square feet plot with independent entrance and three sides open . ( plot size varies with the location of the plot in the project ) <br />
                                    The 5BHK villa comes with a ownership of a 2400  square feet plot with independent entrance and four sides open , giving it the look and feel of a independent bungalow.  ( plot size varies with the location of the plot in the project )<br /><br /> 

                                    <b>2. What is the project completion date ?</b><br><br>

                                    We work in a very structured way. We have engaged the best professionals from the construction industry.<br />
                                    Be it the contractors or the designers of the villas  or the architects or the project management consultant or the power and water management consultants or the Vaastu consultants. <br />
                                    We have calendar schedule as per which the first phase of the project will get completed by 15th July 2017. But we are keeping some grace period to complete it before 31st December 2017. <br />
                                    Any villa will be delivered within 18 months from the date of booking the villa. <br />
                                    This will be the fastest ever constructed project in and around Shahapur. The only reason for this is, the professionals on board and the complete project planning which has happened way before the construction begins. . Even the material for the entire project have already been selected and all working drawings are in place.<br /><br />
                    
                                    <b>3. What is the exact location of the project ?</b><br><br>
                    
                                    The project is just around 500 metres from the main NH-3 Highway  because of which the project is almost pollution free and noise-free. People today prefer the convenience of the location in Terms of travel comforts and along with pollution free environment and also the luxury of being in a noise free situation and away from the honking traffic. <br />
                                    This project is well placed and located for making a  luxury project happen in one of the best locations of Shahapur which is just below 15  km Radius from the prominent Religious Locations of the vicinity.<br /><br />
                                    <strong>LOCATION</strong><br />
                                    THE WHITE VILLAS  is approx 45 km from thane and approx 75 km from mumbai. Atgaon railway station is just 3 km away from the site. <br />
                                    The famous MANAS MANDIR and GURUDWARA SAHIB SHAHAPUR , are two very internationally renowned religious spots which are very close by and have added to the value of Shahapur and surrounding areas. <br />
                                    The hill station IGATPURI is just 55 km away. Nashik city is 102 km away and Shirdi is 175 km away. <br />
                                    The travel distance from mumbai to THE WHITE VILLAS is below  100 minutes, depending on the time of the travel. The roads are brand new and broad for an efficient travel and is being known as one of the fastest well developed roads around mumbai. <br /><br />
                    
                                    <b>4. What are the arrangements of water and power in terms of regular supply ?</b> <br><br>
                    
                                    There is a senior water management consultant , who is one of the best dealers for Kirloskars, who has planned the water storage and water supply in a manner where water will be available to the complex 24/7.  <br />
                                    We have our own water source and a water treatment / purification unit will ensure good quality water 24/7.   <br />
                                    The villa would get water from two sources. A independent overhead water tank per villa and a common water storage tank for the whole complex.   <br />
                                    Our electrical planning experts and electrical contractors will ensure best quality of wiring and a backup of a generator which will be of optimum size to ensure continuous supply of electricity in case of any government related power cut or short supply, to some key points of the villa. <br />
                                    We understand that water and power supply are two very important aspects of any residential complex. And we have taken the extra mile to make sure these two issues are addressed well.   <br />
                                    Power and water supply are problems all across the country. We are ensuring that these two points are well taken care of. <br />
                                    For the power management , the generator will support lights and fans in the Villa to make sure that the comforts of the Villa owners are not compromised.<br /><br />

                    
                                    <b>5. What are the details of the clubhouse ?</b><br><br>
                    
                                    We are providing an 1800 sq.ft built up  independent two level club house so that there is no disturbance / nuisance to the villa owners.  Indoor Games like table tennis, chess, carrom board etc can also be played in the clubhouse. <br />
                                    The gym will also be a part of this clubhouse. <br />
                                    The amenity area is a total of 8880 sqft of open plot with good lawns and lighting and which would be used for family and friends celebrations for the villa owners. <br /><br />
                    
                                    <b>6. What about the entrance to the Project ?</b><br><br>
                    
                                    The entrance to THE WHITE VILLAS is well secured and with well designed, elegant gates and esthetically planned lights. The entrance itself would also be a piece of art adding value to the overall Project. Ms. Sussanne has ensured that everything, including the grand entrance , should be a piece of art. <br />
                                    The overall Project is also well protected with a tall compound wall around the whole Project. <br /><br />
                                                        
                                    <b>7. India is prone to the mosquito problem. What are the precautions you are taking ?</b><br><br>
                    
                                    The project is being made on international standards. The sewage and drainage management are being done in a way where there wouldn't be any problems in the future which might lead to foul smell or stagnant water which breeds mosquitoes. <br />
                                    The exteriors of the project and the non constructed areas are also going to be made in a maintenance free mode. There won't be any water logging situations nor would be there any possibility of stagnating water. <br />
                                    The entire construction is being planned In a way which will be easy to be maintained by the society after the handover happens. This will ensure that no rodents or mosquitoes become a menace for the villa owners.<br /><br />
                    
                                    <b>8. What about the access roads and vehicle movement and car parking ?</b><br><br>
                    
                                    Every Villas has dedicated Parking at the Entrance of the villa. And the internal roads are 9meters wide for smooth movement of vehicles.<br />
                                    The entire project is a gated community and the access to the complex will be well protected and guarded. <br />
                                    Within the complex there is a provision of parking for guests of the 43 Villas As all roads internally are very broad and spacious and parking on the internal roads won't be a hassle to anyone. <br /><br />
                    
